text: Alexander Robertson "Duke" Wellington (August 4, 1893 – September 20, 1967) was a Canadian professional ice hockey player. Wellington played senior ice hockey and one game in the National Hockey League for the Quebec Bulldogs during the 1919–20 NHL season. ==Other websites== * Category:1893 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Canadian ice hockey right wingers Category:Ice hockey people from Ontario Category:Sportspeople from Thunder Bay Category:Quebec Bulldogs players
